      "text": "This right here is part of the problem. A tiny portion of the people ICE attempts to apprehend are violent criminals, but the entire narrative has boiled down into a small but loud portion of our population making the correlation that all immigrants are evil monsters and dehumanizing them.\n\nThat of course results in the stance that anyone who opposes ICE automatically supports violent criminals and sexual predators, which leads them to be demonized and the divide widens.\n\nNobody supports violent criminals being here. The whole problem is that people's Constitutional rights are being violated in the process, and THAT is where the focus needs to be.\n\nCertain ICE agents are also violent criminals, and that has resulted in the loss of American lives, so let's stop pretending this is about deportation.",
      "text_resolved": "This right here is part of the problem. A tiny portion of the people ICE attempts to apprehend are violent criminals, but the entire narrative has boiled down into a small but loud portion of our population making the correlation that all immigrants are evil monsters and dehumanizing them.\n\nThat of course results in the stance that anyone who opposes ICE automatically supports violent criminals and sexual predators, which leads them to be demonized and the divide widens.\n\nNobody supports violent criminals being here. The whole problem is that people's Constitutional rights are being violated in the process, and THAT is where the focus needs to be.\n\nCertain ICE agents are also violent criminals, and that has resulted in the loss of American lives, so let's stop pretending this is about deportation.",
